exponent or power
mathematical notation above base that indicate number of time quantities multiplied by itself

exponent base
bottom number being multiplied by itself

multiplication
repeated addition of same number

decrease in exponent
divide product / exponent base to solve for previous product

zeroth power
any base raised to power of zero equal 1

how to calculate exponent of decimal
each number multiplied after decimal point result in moving decimal point to left that number of time

how to calculate exponent of fraction
product of both numerator/ product of both denominator

direction of operation
calculate left to right

addition & subtraction
order does not matter

multiplication & division
order does matter
